---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Emergency Services | Medical Care and Rehabilitation"
  description="Learn about emergency medical services available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Understand how to access urgent care and support in crisis situations.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Emergency Services for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) ensures that veterans have access to emergency medical services when needed. This page outlines the emergency services available and provides guidance on how to access urgent care in crisis situations.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Immediate Medical Emergencies</h2>
        <p>For life-threatening emergencies:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Call 999 or go to the nearest A&E department</li>
          <li>Inform medical staff of your veteran status for appropriate care</li>
          <li>AFCS liaison officers available in major hospitals</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Urgent Mental Health Support</h2>
        <p>For mental health crises:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>24/7 Veterans Mental Health Helpline: 0800 XXX XXXX</li>
          <li>Access to emergency psychiatric evaluations</li>
          <li>Crisis intervention teams specialised in veteran care</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Service-Related Injury Flare-Ups</h2>
        <p>For sudden worsening of service-related conditions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Dedicated hotline for urgent care coordination: 0800 XXX XXXX</li>
          <li>Fast-track appointments with specialists</li>
          <li>Emergency home visits for mobility-impaired veterans</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Telehealth Emergency Services</h2>
        <p>Remote emergency support:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Video consultations with emergency care providers</li>
          <li>24/7 online chat support for urgent medical advice</li>
          <li>Remote monitoring for veterans with chronic conditions</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Emergency Dental Services</h2>
        <p>For urgent dental care needs:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to out-of-hours dental services</li>
          <li>Emergency dental treatments covered under AFCS</li>
          <li>Specialist care for service-related dental injuries</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Post-Emergency Follow-Up</h2>
        <p>Ensuring continuity of care after emergencies:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Automatic scheduling of follow-up appointments</li>
          <li>Coordination with regular healthcare providers</li>
          <li>Review of care plans and AFCS benefits if needed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Emergency Contacts</h3>
            <p><strong>Medical Emergencies:</strong> 999</p>
            <p><strong>Mental Health Crisis:</strong> 0800 XXX XXXX</p>
            <p><strong>Urgent Care Coordination:</strong> 0800 XXX XXXX</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/medical/mental-health-care" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Care</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/specialist-treatments" class="text-decoration-none">Specialist Treatments</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/crisis-assistance" class="text-decoration-none">Crisis Assistance</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
